des: The Best of EKR’s Rock Radio Format, without DJ’s, from the late 60’s until the mid 90’s with Classic Rock and songs from unsigned Bands of that era. “This rock radio station is all about the music”. Drawing on a vast database of classic, current and unsigned rock bands we are pushing the boundaries of the classic rock radio format to a new, fresh and inspirational level.
